---
title: Smoked Salmon Brunch Tart Serves 2 | with Capers and Chive Cream Cheese
description: All the deliciousness of a bagel with lox in an elegant tart for brunch! Swoops of herby cream cheese, whipped with sour cream, make a luscious base for smoky salmon, perky pickled onions and briny capers!
